narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Unless you are prepared to constantly have standards of engagement change and want to have your Friday afternoon take up (you don't realize how valuable this is until its too late), don't take this class.
yes! fun and low workload class (since it is half credit after all)
Only if the student is sure they are interested. The class is a full year which is difficult because it leaves little room for course options for second semester.
You learn of a variety of fields, so it being a year-long course isn't daunting at all. LOVE THE COURSE, RANK IT
